== 1.2.1 ==

* fix rmagick/minimagic compatibility issue
* fix paperclip crop parameters handling

== 1.2.0 ==

* fix image refresh after crop
* only use carrierwave when both paperclip and carrierwave exist
* work with both rails 3/4

== 1.1.2 ==

